      <ul>
        <li>Your income information</li>
        <li>Child care provider details</li>
        <li>Proof of Alberta residency</li>
      </ul>

      <GoabCallout type="information" heading="Privacy notice">
        Information collected is used to assess your eligibility under the Child Care Subsidy Act.
        For questions, contact the FOIP Coordinator.
